At present within the OfficeConnector plugin, the value for the {{DefaultTemporaryAuthTokenManager}} is hard-coded to ten (10) minutes. This was discovered earlier this year as a result of earlier investigation. Clients would like to be able to configure the value to either smaller or larger amount of time, providing better flexibility for them to configure the token for their own needs and security requirements. 

